<HEAD>

<TITLE>Town Hall Spotlight: Bosnia - Is It Worth It?</TITLE>

</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/paper2.jpg">  
<P>

<CENTER><a name="intro"></a> 

<H2>The Bosnia Mission - Is It Worth it?<BR></CENTER></H2>

This week, President Clinton is sending thousands of U.S. Troops to Bosnia to make peace and not everyone agrees on the goals, reasons, or if we should even be in Bosnia.  This week, Town Hall has assembled several pieces of information from around the net and here at Town Hall.  Check back every day for new additions and later in the week, give us your opinion of the Bosnia mission.
<P>


<P>
<P>


<HR>

<P><a name="week"></a>

<CENTER><b><a name="Misc">Bosnia</a></b> <br>

</center><p>

<p>
<ul>
<li>Read the Heritage Foundation's paper <a href="/heritage/library/categories/forpol/bg1062.html">Questioning the Bosnia Peace Plan</a> by John Hillen. -- Backgrounder #1062<P>
<li>National Review exclusive on Clinton's deal with the Russians.<a href="/nationalreview/11dec95/yalta.htm">Yalta in the Balkans</a><p>

<li>Read Jeane Kirkpatrick's <a href="/empower/ct-11155.html">comments</a> on U.S. troops in Bosnia
<P>
<li>Check out the <a href="http://www.dtic.dla.mil/bosnia/">BosniaLink</a> site from the Pentagon<p>
<li>Check out the home pages of the <a href="http://www.un.org">United Nations</a> and <a href="http://www.nato.int">NATO</a>.<P>
<li>Check the <a href="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/Bosnia/index.html">"Balkan Daily Update"</a> from CNN Interactive.<P>
<li>Read Family Research Council President <a href="/townhall/FRC/radio/c95k29.html">Gary Bauer's Daily Commentary</a> on "Bosnia"
<P>
<li><a href="/heritage/library/categories/forpol/em437.html">Clinton Fails To Make the Case For American Troops In Bosnia</a> by John Hillen. (Executive Memorandum #437)
<P>
