Sending U.S. Troops to Bosnia</a> by John Hillen. (F.Y.I. #66)
<P>
<LI><a href="/heritage/library/categories/forpol/bgup262.html">The Risks of
Clinton's Bosnia Peace Plan</a> by John Hillen. (Backgrounder Update #262)
<P>



</ul>
