http://www.cpac.org:80/empower/new/bennett.htm 204.71.237.74 19970109101440 text/html 3631
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 10:14:32 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 25-Jul-96 20:48:28 GMT
