<DOCNO>WT19-B26-218</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA055-000920-B011-108</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/pff/aspen-mv.html 204.71.237.74 19970109111234 text/html 16716
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 11:12:45 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 11-Jul-96 19:36:21 GMT
Content-length: 16528
