<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT19-B26-319</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA086-000618-B012-468</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/library/categories/forpol/econ_index/tan.html.cgi 204.71.237.74 19970121233518 text/html 5228
